 evade sinister forces to uncover the shocking truth behind the theater\u2019s dark history.\n\nThe Atlas Mystery combines challenging escape-room style puzzles with a riveting investigative narrative full of shocking twists and haunting revelations, plunging players into a detailed and captivating world inspired by classic cinema. ", "short_description": "Explore the haunted halls of the infamous Atlas Theater, a 1940\u2019s era movie palace that played host to a shocking Hollywood tragedy. Solve intricate puzzles, discover startling artifacts, and evade sinister forces to uncover the twisted truth behind the theater\u2019s dark history."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://www.atlasmystery.com/privacy-policy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "https://www.atlasmystery.com/terms-of-service", "publisher_name": "TRC DMI", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://www.atlasmystery.com/", "category": "GAMES", "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "2691890164460465"}, {"id": "377978390272490"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["EXPLORATION", "PUZZLE", "STRATEGY"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["ROOM_SCALE", "STANDING", "SITTING"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "1099564924223989"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 2, "nodes": [{"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "926086922728536"}, {"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "528759491962527"}]}, "baseline_offer": {"id": "528759491962527"}, "is_approved": true, "firstOffer": {"nodes": [{"start_time": 1734372000, "status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "9260869227